{"tid":1822227,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"成日都話學校係社會嘅縮影","createTime":"2020-01-12T21:39:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T23:34:00.000Z","uid":123151,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c309b3a12470c47f487193199ebacb50c9b44fac","tid":1822227,"uid":123151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T21:39:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n學生會同老師校長提議學校旅行去北京<br />\n<br />\n有一部分同學極之反對要求撤回，話北京空氣差食物又唔安全又冇嘢好玩<br />\n<br />\n有一部分就話好呀唔錯，但其實淨係睇過北京旅遊書話點好點好，話上面嗰啲同學喺度亂講嘢<br />\n<br />\n有一部分就冇表態，總之唔好搞到我讀書<br />\n<br />\n咁唔想去北京嘅同學就日日小息、放學喺操場坐嗌口號話唔想去呀，寧願唔去學校旅行好過，仲諗住去圍學生會啦<br />\n<br />\n咁老師就叫風紀去守秩序，但唔知發生咩事，明明學生會出面係有嗰地方俾同學發表意見嘅，而家就話唔俾入喎，咁啲同學梗係嬲啦，咪衝入去囉<br />\n<br />\n啲風紀就梗係唔俾啦，老師叫落要班同學有秩序㗎嘛，加上「唔聽我話我咪好冇面，咁我同普通學生有咩分別，加上我有權捉你哋去訓導記缺點」嘅想法，演變左好耐嘅「戰爭」(詞窮，好似有啲誇張)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeb4a1b7efc232f0300d3c044251fb1bdcc81a31","tid":1822227,"uid":123151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T21:41:11.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"0edad534e12a1efa1ddcf71240ddabcc83a1a18a","tid":1822227,"uid":123151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T21:42:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77371f889be955ff6086026ca656ce4ba143dc0b","tid":1822227,"uid":57767,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T21:43:23.000Z","msg":"呢個比喻太差，去旅行點同送中比，再講又比喻唔到警暴<br />\n<br />\n你將去旅行比喻做去做洗廁所，唔俾入比喻做體罰會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9471d19c16053454c25a4f5dae7fc909a9ca0f50","tid":1822227,"uid":123151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"77371f889be955ff6086026ca656ce4ba143dc0b","tid":1822227,"uid":57767,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T21:43:23.000Z","msg":"呢個比喻太差，去旅行點同送中比，再講又比喻唔到警暴<br />\n<br />\n你將去旅行比喻做去做洗廁所，唔俾入比喻做體罰會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T21:47:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ea64ae403332d76b1639e148e15f6100932905d","tid":1822227,"uid":57767,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T21:47:47.000Z","msg":"再講，學校根本就係獨裁同無自由<br />\n叫你去旅行有得say no咩<br />\n<br />\n要話佢地知普世價值係民主自由人權<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdefe3ae0a3563177e63a3421aec999350c36389","tid":1822227,"uid":57767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T21:53:38.000Z","msg":"俾佢地睇下721立場姐姐俾人打條片同701訪問點解要同手足一齊走果條片仲好<br />\n<br />\n太細個未必明咩道理，特別係成家都藍<br />\n人性既野會易啲理解<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5990cb6385ae3056aaeadc2627c374eca23ba315","tid":1822227,"uid":123151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7ea64ae403332d76b1639e148e15f6100932905d","tid":1822227,"uid":57767,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T21:47:47.000Z","msg":"再講，學校根本就係獨裁同無自由<br />\n叫你去旅行有得say no咩<br />\n<br />\n要話佢地知普世價值係民主自由人權<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T22:00:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acdacc6c8fcc31a5bb064ea317fa9c1c8bccbfd7","tid":1822227,"uid":123151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bdefe3ae0a3563177e63a3421aec999350c36389","tid":1822227,"uid":57767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T21:53:38.000Z","msg":"俾佢地睇下721立場姐姐俾人打條片同701訪問點解要同手足一齊走果條片仲好<br />\n<br />\n太細個未必明咩道理，特別係成家都藍<br />\n人性既野會易啲理解<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T22:02:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff640893eedc809be59e6ccfd49f31